      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EYESEALITTLE (5) failed to flatter last time out when seventh, beaten 15 metres, over 2200m at Horsham. Her recent effort is not a true indication. Good enough to take out a race like this. SORRISO DE PRAIA (8) resumes from a spell of three-and-a-half months after closing off last campaign in good form, the last run being a solid third over 2240m at Swan Hill. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon. Likely to run a big race to kick off this campaign. NO EMOTION (3) finished sixth last start over 2190m at Maryborough. Generally runs very well at this circuit so can play a big role. HUNGRY HOGARTH (4) is worth some thought based on his second over 1609m at this track two runs ago.",
